just_use events.go

# label: TINY
# role: holds the GameSetup "photo" struct — first event of every game

Post-rip (2026-04-21) this file carries only `GameSetup`. The
diff-based host dispatch (`CheckEvent`, `ParseMoveEvent`,
`ReconstructBoard`, `wire*` internal types) was deleted after
the grep showed zero live callers; the current session flow is
action-based via `wire_action.go` and `replay.go`.

Kept here rather than in `card_stack.go` or `dealer.go`
because `GameSetup` spans `Card` + `CardStack` + `Hands` +
`Deck` and doesn't belong to any single domain type.
